Large-Scale Transcriptomics-Driven Approach Revealed Overexpression of CRNDE as 
a Poor Survival Prognosis Biomarker in Glioblastoma.

Sorokin M(1)(2)(3), Raevskiy M(3), Zottel A(4), Šamec N(4), Skoblar Vidmar M(5), 
Matjašič A(6), Zupan A(6), Mlakar J(6), Suntsova M(2), Kuzmin DV(3), Buzdin 
