Impact of Comorbidities, Sarcopenia, and Nutritional Status on the Long-Term 
Outcomes after Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection for Early Gastric Cancer in 
Elderly Patients Aged ≥ 80 Years.

Kim GH(1), Choi KD(1), Ko Y(2), Park T(3), Kim KW(3), Park SY(4), Na HK(1), Ahn 
JY(1), Lee JH(1), Jung KW(1), Kim DH(1), Song HJ(1), Lee GH(1), Jung HY(1).

Author information:
(1)Asan Medical Center, Department of Gastroenterology, University of Ulsan 
College of Medicine, Seoul 05505, Korea.
(2)Biomedical Reseach Center, Asan Institute for Life Sciences, University of 
Ulsan College of Medicine, Seoul 05505, Korea.
(3)Asan Medical Center, Department of Radiology, University of Ulsan College of 
